text:
YUMMY POPIAH.

Came here for tze char and decided to try the popiah from KELLY. Very nice. Chock full of ingredients but too much. Friendly service and just good, honest popiah with no nonsense!

RECOMMEND!
👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻
The food is very flavourful and looks very appetising. Popiah can be vegetarian. Stall owners have very good personality and jokes along. Worth my money
